{
  "stem": "6526.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So a lot of people threw the belt away because the double belt had money.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We got off the train, the, the SS, the police-- the German police.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were the German police-- the German-- Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were other ones, the Latvians, Lithuanians, the Poles and all the guards that were guarding us, that were taking us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They brought us up to Majdanek.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then Majdanek, as I mentioned, we went into the bath to give us a bath.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Before taking a bath-- and they took away the clothes, because we were with getting in camp clothes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "At Majdanek, we did not get striped clothes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We got clothes from different people, because they did not want to because-- give us the same clothes, because we came in loused.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had lice on us, because they were so clean, the Germans, they did not want to touch you.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they, they-- we had to leave the clothes and get other ones.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we had the [INAUDIBLE], and this is how we got into the camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There, there were-- in, in Majdanek, there were a few-- a few-- a few places, two or three that I remember, two or three places.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And when I came to Majdanek, a few days later, maybe-- not a few days, maybe two, three weeks later, I found out that my brother is there.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because when he went in across the street, and we, we lived [INAUDIBLE], to find out what happened to the neighbors, the Germans were there and caught them all and sent them to Majdanek.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he was already there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in Majdanek, they were sending away transports.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were taking some of the people that were down, gassed, or little-- with-- unhealthy.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
